highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #46.
“你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 3162 days straight.
“Winter Ahead (with PARK HYO SHIN)” by V and Park Hyo Shin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 75 spots at #94.
“Tears” by Sabrina Carpenter is the highest new entry on Top Songs Singapore at #154.
